#  AI-Powered Color Detection App

This project is an interactive tool built using Python and OpenCV that detects the name of a color when a user selects a pixel in an image. It converts RGB values into LAB color space and finds the closest matching color from a dataset using perceptual color distance.

---

##  Features

- Upload any image and select a pixel to detect its color
- Converts RGB to LAB for perceptual color matching
- Matches to the closest human-readable color name using a custom dataset
- Works entirely in **Google Colab**
- Lightweight, accurate, and easy to use

