##  Dataset

We used the **XKCD Color Survey Dataset** for color name mapping.  
You can find it here:  
ðŸ”— https://github.com/meodai/color-names

Each color entry includes:
- Color name
- RGB values
- Optional HEX values

---

##  Algorithm Overview

1. Load image and dataset
2. Convert selected pixel's RGB values to LAB color space
3. Compute the Euclidean distance between the pixel and each color in the dataset
4. Return the color name with the shortest LAB distance

